   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>DoHom13.1 (mss. 2000, 2035):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            āiryaman abar guftan tā sar <em>isat̰.vāstrahe</em> guftan tā <em>yeŋhe.hātąm</em> tā <em>ahurəm mazdąm</em> kardag ī wisperad guftan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He should the Airyaman until the end, recite <em>isat̰.vāstrahe</em> until the end until the <em>yeŋhe.hātąm</em> and then until the <em>kardag</em> of the Visperad 
            (that begins with ) <em>ahurəm mazdąm</em>"</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
